About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

We'll discuss when and why you should or should not start investing in the stock market, how to choose the right companies to invest in, and which ones to avoid. 05:02 How to invest profitably?
06:39 Think about investing in products you actually use

----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.title: 6 Reasons keeping you POOR | The Middle Class Trap
snippet.description:
▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀

Download Stable Money app, check your emergency fund, book FD at highest Interest rates
https://sm.lla.in
▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀▀

Like most of us, i also come from a middle class family and i have seen how we get stuck in the middle class race, unable to break free and achieve true wealth. Wealth is not just money, it's money + happiness + stability. In this video i attempt to breakdown the root cause of this failure. These are rather 6 big decisions of your life that decide your future and there is a stark contrast between how a middle class person takes these decisions vs how a wealthy person takes them. I hope you get some value from this video.

              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.
